attributes.title: Doesn’t work
attributes.review: After a whole hour of trying, I could not get the app to work. My screen turned black so I just pressed the on/off button because I thought it had turned off. After all of that I just plugged in my phone thinking that it had died. The only thing that had died was my belief that paranormal activity was fake. After downloading this app I saw George Floyd and other dead black people all killed while Trump is president. I really wanted the voices to stop so I decided to delete the app. After realizing what the voices were trying to tell me I quickly changed my mind about Donald J. Trump. I do not support Trump 2020 and hope someone as good of a president as Obama was is president next. Now say it with me 💅🏽🥀🧚‍♂️💋✨💫F*ck Trump 💗❣️💫🧚‍♀️🥀💋✌🏼✨
